<paragraph blockId="5.[215,1379,385,629]" pageId="5" pageNumber="166">
<keyLead pageId="5" pageNumber="166">2a[1]. Trichomes relatively thin-walled with a broad lumen (&gt; ⅓ of cell diameter); uni- or multicellular; surface ornamented ........................................................................................................................................... 3</keyLead>
